{"tid":1386012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet晒腿襲港　狂擦點心睇夜景","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T18:28:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":22,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a2b72a4ec6f0cec7a99d6fe0dda4ebaed07d65","tid":1386012,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190730/photo/bkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190730162854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190730%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190730162854&h=d13f55e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（左起）Joy、Yeri、Irene、Seulgi與Wendy現身記者會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190730/photo/bkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190730162854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190730%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190730162854&h=8921fccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWendy亦以短裙晒腿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190730/photo/bkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190730162854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190730%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190730162854&h=080499ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190730/photo/bkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190730162854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190730%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190730162854&h=391cae9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJoy露腰也很性感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190730/photo/bkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190730162854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190730%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190730160904546-0730_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190730162854&h=b839cbbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIrene身穿短裙晒長腿。<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團Red Velvet今午以免稅店代言人在富豪機場酒店舉行記者會，5名成員先以韓文作自我介紹，問到來港最想品嚐甚麼美食或去甚麼地方觀光，Seulgi指最喜歡吃蛋撻和飲奶茶，Joy就最愛吃點心，笑指昨天和今天都有食點心，Wendy則表示兒時曾來港坐過山頂纜車，印象十分深刻，希望下次來港能和隊友一起去坐。<br />\n<br />\n問到如可在香港一日遊，會想去甚麼地方時，Seulgi就指香港的建築物和街道都很美，想去看看夜景和逛夜市，品嚐香港的地道美食，當主持問到如有兩星期假期，想如何運用時，Seulgi便指因為香港的夜景很美麗，看兩星期也不會嫌，所以想再來香港旅行，又透露昨晚有與Irene去看香港的高樓大廈，Irene更指因為香港的夜景太靚，令她開心到跳起舞來。<br />\n<br />\n談到夏天的護膚心得和流行妝容，Red Velvet就指保濕和防曬最重要，每日都會敷面膜及多飲水，而妝容則會選擇較淡的妝，會用唇膏和胭脂來點綴。而問到除了唱歌以外，想挑戰甚麼範疇時，Joy就笑指想考車牌，Seulgi與Yeri則想開畫展及寫歌。她們亦談到今後想合作的歌手，其中Seulgi希望有機會與同門師姐BoA同台演出，Yeri則想和美國流行樂壇天后Ariana Grande見面，希望可以與對方吃飯和合作出歌。<br />\n<br />\n記者會後，Red Velvet便現身機場二號客運大樓出席免稅店開幕一周年的慶祝活動，現場聚集逾200名粉絲，Red Velvet演唱《Red Flavour》、《Power Up》、《RBB》及《Zimzalabim》四首歌曲，並透露正在準備新碟，希望之後有機會來港開騷。"},{"pid":"14594446e8bd3cb4c1637a1a269bcb2d3c16f016","tid":1386012,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0db860727f83122f016f3fe1b4c6e0ae791e7","tid":1386012,"uid":35014,"like":26,"dislike":39,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182f31516d58ebc1259b6dda54cbb0f285729831","tid":1386012,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"好正..."},{"pid":"30d74098bdd9361ebf6b536509e921c6c78ff873","tid":1386012,"uid":208486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgm